{"tid":544231,"cid":26,"subCid":0,"title":"招識Programming人 一齊合作做個大project","createTime":"2018-01-29T10:07:16.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-31T12:16:54.000Z","uid":87988,"like":68,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"88d789cc807ee7bea1b0ba89f940cc7e0cf9a7e8","tid":544231,"uid":87988,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-29T10:07:16.000Z","msg":"話說 我同兩個朋友有條絕世idea 想整隊高達出黎征服地球 <br />\n但我地對整高達呢方面既知識又唔足夠 <br />\n而我地已經寫好左一份好detail既proposal準備征服唔同國家 奈何仲未有最重要既高達<br />\n<strong><em>所以希望係連登呢到搵到1,2個識寫program既人 一齊合作 當係試下都好 </em></strong><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">反正唔成功都無壞 但如果成功就掂啦</span></span><br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">有意請PM 再傾多啲！！！</span></strong><br />\n<br />\nPS. 我地個條team全部依加都係讀緊小學，我地會負責管理同操作高達方面。"},{"pid":"2deaf28712b57f2e5cfb3824963a9cc1e69e8925","tid":544231,"uid":24764,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-29T10:09:23.000Z","msg":"要搵 基拉大和 佢識改高達OS"},{"pid":"0342cceda30feaa18fd8d27074e830fcf369c82a","tid":544231,"uid":21423,"like":19,"dislike":2,"score":17,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-01-29T10:10:20.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"da75ee689d1dbd78773737f41f4ea01f813ad8df","tid":544231,"uid":28563,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"0342cceda30feaa18fd8d27074e830fcf369c82a","tid":544231,"uid":21423,"like":19,"dislike":2,"score":17,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-01-29T10:10:20.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-29T10:14:09.000Z","msg":"it狗肥絲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8fa885e34555ffe73f9b6557e408e11a5dd1a45d","tid":544231,"uid":44071,"like":20,"dislike":0,"score":20,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-29T10:15:16.000Z","msg":"唔好當樓主講笑<br />\n作為 IT 狗<br />\n真實成日聽到呢類建議<br />\n已經去到聽完屌都費事屌既境界<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f414840df9383ecafa9706cfabc3f5ee7ceccb31","tid":544231,"uid":22719,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-29T10:24:40.000Z","msg":"我就係高達"},{"pid":"4def80cda56ad900889dd59cd68e2c9873428dc2","tid":544231,"uid":5020,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-29T10:31:49.000Z","msg":"partner 你講漏咗我地用咗廿幾個鐘寫咗40幾頁proposal<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1b1555a5135f626f3761afce7582d3bd9188962b","tid":544231,"uid":11001,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-29T10:42:53.000Z","msg":"G持 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cb278022d76b173699e5ce9f4e71827b359db70f","tid":544231,"uid":52509,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0342cceda30feaa18fd8d27074e830fcf369c82a","tid":544231,"uid":21423,"like":19,"dislike":2,"score":17,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-01-29T10:10:20.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-29T11:13:50.000Z","msg":"唔記得換account喎"},{"pid":"f78e30db29c7903f3f1421d675cf30cf483fc4e7","tid":544231,"uid":606,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-29T12:25:54.000Z","msg":"是咁的! 本人係一個天生既優秀企業家, 創意有別於常人,但天意弄人,自己沒有編程知識, <br />\n但有一個地上最強idea,呢個idea一定有別於其他廢柴諗既idea!! 果d撚樣太有自信,以為自己好撚勁 <br />\n有別於常人,佢地以為自己諗既idea獨一無二,好撚怕會比人炒襲,但事實上佢地條橋根本唔值錢 <br />\n一撚早已經有人做左, 仲要做得好能過佢。 <br />\n<br />\n但我一定唔係D咁既人, 我係獨一無二, 我既IDEA必定能賺錢!!! 必定能改變世界!!!成為新一代既神。 <br />\n就係因為我太優秀,所以我更加唔可以識寫程式, 因為IT呢d野比狗學, 如果要我讀IT簡直侮辱左我咁完美既肉體 <br />\n所以現在誠徽IT狗同我一齊實驗呢個idea。 <br />\n<br />\n個idea唔方便講, 怕有人炒尻我 <br />\n大約要識既野: <br />\n-要寫網頁, Android, IOS(唔比用類似PhoneGap既軟件生成D垃圾假Apps,屌你老母) <br />\n-有會員系統(要用 facebook, gmail, Active Directory或 高登帳號 登入) <br />\n-信用咭付款 <br />\n-運作暢順, 任何國家用都唔會lag <br />\n-要安全, 難以被hack <br />\n-要一世maintenance <br />\n-7x24 技術支援 (唔撚該你要學7國語言) <br />\n-用任何search engine search都要係第一頁內出現,你老母化西 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n預算筆直: 你係呢個project 所學到既知識就係我預算既筆直 <br />\n你老母化西, 依家係我出我最珍貴Idea比機會你學野, 你仲要問你拎人工!!! <br />\n完成左呢個project之後你所得既一定超過8位數字, 拎住件apps去見工大撚把公司請你, 你做得好仲可以成為新一代既神,改變呢個世界, 諗返轉頭,家陣係我比緊機會你! 應該係你比返錢我呀仆街!!! <br />\n可以同我呢D咁撚優秀既人合作你要好好珍借。 <br />\n<br />\n但又唔係完全冇錢收 <br />\n當呢個project完成左之後, 我負責賣，再齊齊分錢, 即係每賣一件都會分番錢比你，變成你既被動性收入 <br />\n你執撚到!!即係直到你死果日都要錢分比你!!抵撚到仆街啦 <br />\n<br />\n同我合作係你福份, 咪撚再要求咁多, 你唔同合作, 大撚把IT狗同合作,屌你老母臭西仆街臭化撚屌西尻尻"},{"pid":"e4c8c748f139f29a0541edf9ce052771f0d9170f","tid":544231,"uid":75692,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"da75ee689d1dbd78773737f41f4ea01f813ad8df","tid":544231,"uid":28563,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"0342cceda30feaa18fd8d27074e830fcf369c82a","tid":544231,"uid":21423,"like":19,"dislike":2,"score":17,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-01-29T10:10:20.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-29T10:14:09.000Z","msg":"it狗肥絲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-29T14:54:28.000Z","msg":"think he is fake it dog"},{"pid":"cfba759ddd06baf5caa91b2bc1e8866fe4312dbd","tid":544231,"uid":87988,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"f414840df9383ecafa9706cfabc3f5ee7ceccb31","tid":544231,"uid":22719,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-29T10:24:40.000Z","msg":"我就係高達"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-01-30T03:47:33.000Z","msg":"無操作員既高達咪又一件廢物🤗"},{"pid":"d882622838390b63b50ebbad0aaf450997120fbc","tid":544231,"uid":33883,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"cfba759ddd06baf5caa91b2bc1e8866fe4312dbd","tid":544231,"uid":87988,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"f414840df9383ecafa9706cfabc3f5ee7ceccb31","tid":544231,"uid":22719,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-29T10:24:40.000Z","msg":"我就係高達"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-01-30T03:47:33.000Z","msg":"無操作員既高達咪又一件廢物🤗"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-30T11:41:25.000Z","msg":"唔好咁out啦, 高達操作員已成夕陽行業, 畀A.I.吞咗啦! <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"efa1d70743c3231fac2a14837a05e5a6928521fa","tid":544231,"uid":129573,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-30T17:29:30.000Z","msg":"召喚rx-78 巴打<